text: Aicha Sayah is a Moroccan karateka. In 2019, she represented Morocco at the 2019 African Games held in Rabat, Morocco and she won the gold medal in the women's kumite 50 kg event. She also won the gold medal in the women's team kumite event. In 2018, she won the silver medal in the women's kumite 50 kg event at the 2018 Mediterranean Games held in Tarragona, Spain.
